query:
INSERT INTO experiences (activityTypeId, title, slug, shortIntro, description, durationMin, priceFromUsd, includes, excludes, requirements, published, featured, displayOrder) VALUES
(1, '2-Tank Dive', '2-tank-dive', 'Explore underwater wonders', 'Experience two amazing dive sites with certified dive master. Perfect for certified divers.', 180, 65.00, 'Dive equipment, boat, guide, 2 dives', 'Certification course, transportation', 'Valid dive certification (PADI/SSI)', 1, 1, 1),
(1, '4-Tank Dive', '4-tank-dive', 'Full day diving adventure', 'Full day diving experience with 4 dives at premium dive sites. Includes lunch and refreshments.', 360, 120.00, 'Dive equipment, boat, guide, 4 dives, lunch', 'Certification course', 'Valid dive certification', 1, 1, 2),
(1, 'Discover Scuba Diving', 'discover-scuba-diving', 'Learn to dive', 'Beginner-friendly introduction to scuba diving. No certification required.', 240, 100.00, 'Equipment, training, 1 dive', 'Advanced dives', 'Minimum age 10, good health', 1, 1, 3),
(2, 'Snorkeling with Turtles', 'snorkeling-turtles', 'Swim with sea turtles', 'Guided snorkeling tour to see sea turtles in their natural habitat.', 120, 55.00, 'Snorkel gear, boat, guide', 'Lunch', 'Able to swim', 1, 1, 4),
(2, 'Sandbank & Snorkeling', 'sandbank-snorkeling', 'Island and reef exploration', 'Visit pristine sandbank and snorkel at coral gardens with tropical fish.', 180, 75.00, 'Snorkel gear, boat, guide, sandbank visit', 'Lunch', 'Able to swim', 1, 1, 5),
(2, 'Nurse Sharks & Stingrays', 'nurse-sharks-stingrays', 'Unique marine encounters', 'Snorkel with gentle nurse sharks and stingrays in shallow waters.', 240, 90.00, 'Snorkel gear, boat, guide, marine encounters', 'Lunch', 'Able to swim', 1, 1, 6),
(3, 'Sunset Fishing', 'sunset-fishing', 'Evening fishing adventure', 'Traditional Maldivian fishing experience during golden hour sunset.', 120, 60.00, 'Fishing rod, boat, guide, refreshments', 'Catch guarantee', 'Minimum age 8', 1, 1, 7),
(3, 'Night Fishing', 'night-fishing', 'Nocturnal fishing experience', 'Fish under the stars with traditional methods. BBQ dinner included.', 180, 75.00, 'Fishing rod, boat, guide, BBQ dinner', 'Catch guarantee', 'Minimum age 10', 1, 1, 8),
(4, 'Dolphin Cruise', 'dolphin-cruise', 'Marine mammal watching', 'Search for dolphins and enjoy scenic ocean views from the boat.', 120, 50.00, 'Boat, guide, refreshments', 'Guarantee sightings', 'None', 1, 1, 9),
(4, 'Whale Shark Encounter', 'whale-shark-encounter', 'Swim with gentle giants', 'Seasonal opportunity to snorkel with whale sharks (seasonal: May-November).', 240, 150.00, 'Boat, guide, snorkel gear', 'Guarantee sightings', 'Able to swim', 1, 0, 10),
(5, 'Island Hopping Tour', 'island-hopping-tour', 'Multi-island exploration', 'Visit 2-3 local islands with cultural experiences and beach time.', 360, 85.00, 'Boat, guide, island visits', 'Meals', 'None', 1, 1, 11),
(5, 'Local Island Experience', 'local-island-experience', 'Authentic island life', 'Spend time on a local inhabited island, meet locals, explore community.', 240, 65.00, 'Boat, guide, island access', 'Meals', 'None', 1, 1, 12),
(6, 'Water Sports Combo', 'water-sports-combo', 'Adventure on water', 'Jet ski, kayaking, and tubing in one thrilling package.', 180, 110.00, 'Equipment, boat, guide', 'Meals', 'Minimum age 12', 1, 1, 13),
(6, 'Kayaking Tour', 'kayaking-tour', 'Peaceful paddling', 'Guided kayaking through lagoons and coral gardens.', 120, 45.00, 'Kayak, guide, life jacket', 'Meals', 'Able to swim', 1, 1, 14),
(7, 'Male City Tour', 'male-city-tour', 'Capital city exploration', 'Guided tour of Male with visits to mosque, markets, and local shops.', 180, 50.00, 'Guide, transportation', 'Meals', 'None', 1, 1, 15),
(8, 'Sunset Cruise', 'sunset-cruise', 'Romantic evening experience', 'Relax on a boat with drinks and snacks while watching the sunset.', 120, 65.00, 'Boat, guide, refreshments', 'Meals', 'None', 1, 1, 16)
